if you get error name is too longs ..just chnage the kafka folder name kafka 3.2 .1 to kafka
create folder data folder and 
C:\Users\13033\Desktop\softwares\kafka\data
inside data create another 2 folders
kafka and zookeeper
edit zooker properties file 
dataDir=C:/Users/13033/Desktop/softwares/kafka/data/zookeeper
and server.properties as 
# A comma separated list of directories under which to store log files
log.dirs=C:/Users/13033/Desktop/softwares/kafka/data/kafka

now create two cmd file s
cd C:\Users\13033\Desktop\softwares\kafka\bin\windows
zookeeper-server-start C:\Users\13033\Desktop\softwares\kafka\config\zookeeper.properties

and 

cd C:\Users\13033\Desktop\softwares\kafka\bin\windows
kafka-server-start C:\Users\13033\Desktop\softwares\kafka\config\server.properties
